calculatedFields.name: rec_sort_key
calculatedFields.expression:
parseInt(
concat(
toString(extract('YYYY', {received_date})),
ifelse(
strlen(toString(extract('MM', {received_date}))) = 1,
concat('0', toString(extract('MM', {received_date}))),
toString(extract('MM', {received_date}))
),
ifelse(
strlen(toString(extract('DD', {received_date}))) = 1,
concat('0', toString(extract('DD', {received_date}))),
toString(extract('DD', {received_date}))
)
)
)
